item.description:
Excel is a fantastic tool for quickly accessing, manipulating, and visualizing small-to-medium-sized datasets. However, Excel does not contain many statistical algorithms or tests &ldquo;out of the box.&rdquo;
  As we progress through the curriculum, we will cover a number of more robust statistical functions, tests, and concepts.
  If we enable Excel&rsquo;s Analysis ToolPak add-on, we can always return to Excel to perform statistical tests on smaller datasets.
